&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Adding an upgrade hook for plugin schema migrations
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Documenting how this is to be done
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Find a way to avoid conflicts
